snippet.title: Johnny Depp May Be 'Ostracised From Hollywood' After Amber Heard Divorce Court Case | This Morning
snippet.description:
It’s been one of the most dramatic showbiz trials we’ve ever seen - and now the verdict is in. Today Hollywood star Johnny Depp discovers that he has LOST his blockbuster libel action against the newspaper which labelled him a 'wife beater'. Matthew Wright joins Phil and Holly to discuss the impacts of this result. We are also joined by Sam Rubin to hear the reactions from across the pond and what this could mean for the A-List star's reputation. Former newspaper man and now PR guru Phil Hall strongly believes that Johnny Depp must now clean up his act!
Broadcast on 02/11/20
